    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_3_43508-43576",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "43508-43576",
      "markText": "而我写出它，则纯粹是为了自己的心灵。　　在一个人灵魂中扎下根的，必长出叶子。于读者，便是所谓“小说”了。　　于我，却是心溃之血！",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=43508&rangeEnd=43576",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=43508&rangeEnd=43576"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_20683-20741",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "20683-20741",
      "markText": "母亲走了。带着一身烫伤。失落了她的假牙。留下的，是母亲的临时挂号证，上面草率的字写着眼科医生的诊断——已无手术价值。",
      "totalCount": 1530,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=20683&rangeEnd=20741",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=20683&rangeEnd=20741"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_2-73",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2-73",
      "markText": "淫雨在户外哭泣，瘦叶在窗前瑟缩。这一个孤独的日子，我想念我的母亲。有三只眼睛隔窗瞅我，都是那杨树的眼睛。愣愣地呆呆地瞅我，我觉得那是一种凝视。",
      "totalCount": 1496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=73",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=73"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_3102-3122",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "3102-3122",
      "markText": "生活没能将母亲变成懊丧的怨天怨地的女人。",
      "totalCount": 1442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=3102&rangeEnd=3122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=3102&rangeEnd=3122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_2_10244-10269",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "10244-10269",
      "markText": "小姨说：“人活着嘛，就得想着法儿让自己活得舒畅！”",
      "totalCount": 1440,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=10244&rangeEnd=10269",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=10244&rangeEnd=10269"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_6063-6130",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "6063-6130",
      "markText": "母亲听得认真。凡此种种，母亲总先默默听，不打断我们的话，耐心而怜悯的样子。直至她的儿女们觉得没什么补充的了，母亲才平静地作出她的结论。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6063&rangeEnd=6130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6063&rangeEnd=6130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_3_2-54",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2-54",
      "markText": "没姐姐，对男孩儿来说，是一大缺憾。这如同先天的色盲，世界在他眼里，少了某种颜色。当然，她须是一位好姐姐。",
      "totalCount": 1040,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=54",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=54"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_14100-14144",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "14100-14144",
      "markText": "他却是去拦截了一辆小汽车，对司机大声说：“把那个女人和孩子送回家去。要一直送到家门口！”",
      "totalCount": 1035,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=14100&rangeEnd=14144",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=14100&rangeEnd=14144"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_15839-15906",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "15839-15906",
      "markText": "那一天我第一次发现，我的母亲原来是那么瘦小，竟快是一个老女人了！那时刻我努力要回忆起一个年轻的母亲的形象，竟回忆不起母亲她何时年轻过。",
      "totalCount": 1024,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=15839&rangeEnd=15906",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=15839&rangeEnd=15906"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_1055-1095",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1055-1095",
      "markText": "与其说母亲是在讲给我们几个孩子听，莫如说更是在自言自语，更是一种回忆的特殊方式。",
      "totalCount": 980,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1055&rangeEnd=1095",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1055&rangeEnd=1095"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_3_37907-37943",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "37907-37943",
      "markText": "秋天是最辉煌的季节，也是最短暂的季节，短暂得仿佛首尾被夏与冬克扣了似的。",
      "totalCount": 910,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=37907&rangeEnd=37943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=37907&rangeEnd=37943"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_15732-15777",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "15732-15777",
      "markText": "母亲却已将钱塞在我手心里了，大声回答那个女人：“谁叫我们是当妈的啊！我挺高兴他爱看书的！”",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=15732&rangeEnd=15777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=15732&rangeEnd=15777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_2622-2693",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2622-2693",
      "markText": "小妹用两根手指将母亲的落发从我手中捏过去，神态异样地细瞧，接着放在母亲留于枕上的深深的为汗渍所染的头印中，趴在枕旁，守着。好似守着的是母亲……",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2622&rangeEnd=2693",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2622&rangeEnd=2693"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_6373-6404",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "6373-6404",
      "markText": "而母亲的逻辑是善良的逻辑，包含有一个似无争亦似无奈的“忍”字。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6373&rangeEnd=6404",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6373&rangeEnd=6404"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_1245-1279",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1245-1279",
      "markText": "我们扯着母亲褪色的衣襟长大成人。在贫困中她尽了一位母亲最大的责任……",
      "totalCount": 828,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1245&rangeEnd=1279",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1245&rangeEnd=1279"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_6134-6233",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "6134-6233",
      "markText": "母亲淡淡地说：“怨你。你该分给他们些啊。你撸了一袋子呀！都是孩子，都挨饿。那么小气，他们还不抢你吗？往后记住，再碰到这种事儿，惹人家动手抢之前，就先主动给，主动分。别人对你满意，你自己也不吃亏……”",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6134&rangeEnd=6233",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6134&rangeEnd=6233"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_9254-9353",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "9254-9353",
      "markText": "“你们都记住，讨饭的人可怜，但不可耻。走投无路的时候，低三下四也没什么。偷和抢，就让人恨了！别人多么恨你们，妈就多么恨你们！除了这一层脸面，妈什么尊贵都没有！你们谁想丢尽妈的脸，就去偷，就去抢……”",
      "totalCount": 780,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=9254&rangeEnd=9353",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=9254&rangeEnd=9353"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_4_35443-35458",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "35443-35458",
      "markText": "世界变红了，包括那朵野菊花……",
      "totalCount": 774,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=35443&rangeEnd=35458",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=35443&rangeEnd=35458"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "44072622_1_836-895",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "836-895",
      "markText": "母亲讲时，眼泪扑簌簌地落。落在手背上，落在衣襟上，也不拭，也不抬头。一针一针，一线一线，缝补我的或弟弟妹妹们的破衣服。",
      "totalCount": 768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=44072622&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=836&rangeEnd=895",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/63132d9072a07eae631c7ef?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=836&rangeEnd=895"
    },
    {
